{"tid":1672431,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對家開始玩裝修？","createTime":"2019-10-24T06:04:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T06:28:28.000Z","uid":271894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"15b8a9f177864ce425d5531c85c34456bad4b1ef","tid":1672431,"uid":271894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:04:10.000Z","msg":"龍門冰室被爆玻璃破壞　市民排隊幫襯力撐<br />\n<br />\n自「反送中」運動開始以來一直支持港人、並推出「學生免費餐」的龍門冰室，紅磡店今晨開舖前（24日）遭破壞，門外櫥窗玻璃被扑爆，又打爛店內閉路電視、兩部收銀電腦和牆上鏡面裝飾，並推翻桌椅。餐廳清理後，今早七時已照常開業，午飯時間店外出現長長人龍。龍門冰室被破壞的消息在網上瘋傳，不少網民留言，指日後要更加把勁「懲罰」該店，努力幫襯支持。<br />\n<br />\nFrom 立場<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2555802211172050?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2555802211172050%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUocpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=b95b6fb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2555802211172050?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"14d65cf88210f21837493e9d9d60b5e3da76fca4","tid":1672431,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:04:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">一、誠意推薦：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃</em></strong><br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUocpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=2e20e620\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUocpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=bac81a58\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">二、什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">三、為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">四、遊說集團？對家一早做緊啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUocpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=8bc53551\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUocpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=e1db5637\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a>"},{"pid":"e3a4824a7ed0284b7e8380980aadb505f26b19dc","tid":1672431,"uid":278990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:28:28.000Z","msg":"懲罰大大力.."}]}